03:26.620 --> 03:30.280
from behind the resolute desk, this place of very serious presidential

03:30.280 --> 03:34.360
addresses. And this was about explaining the very difficult decision he

03:34.360 --> 03:39.000
made to step aside and putting it in a noble light. He was also making an

03:39.000 --> 03:42.560
appeal to the American people to think about what kind of country they

03:42.560 --> 03:46.340
want. At the very end, Biden delivered this emotional expression of

03:46.340 --> 03:49.880
gratitude, saying that he had given his heart and soul to the nation over

03:49.880 --> 03:54.120
50 years in public life and has been blessed with the love and support of

03:54.120 --> 03:58.620
the American people. I hope you have some idea how grateful I am to all of

03:58.620 --> 04:05.180
you. The great thing about America is here, kings and dictators do not

04:05.180 --> 04:09.880
rule, the people do. This wasn't the place for the overtly political

04:09.880 --> 04:13.800
language you would hear at a campaign rally. So he never said former

04:13.800 --> 04:18.220
President Trump's name, but the subtext was quite clear. It was clear, but

04:18.220 --> 04:21.480
you know the speech had the feeling of a farewell address, Tam, but he

04:21.480 --> 04:24.980
still has six months left in office. What did he say he wants to do at the

04:24.980 --> 04:28.760
time he is left? You know, it really felt like the oxygen drained out of

04:28.760 --> 04:31.480
his presidency when he announced he was dropping out of the race for

04:31.480 --> 04:35.740
reelection. But practically speaking, this term was already in a lame duck

04:35.740 --> 04:40.060
phase. His biggest achievements happened before Democrats lost control of

04:40.060 --> 04:44.340
the House in 2023. So a lot of what he can do in these final months is

04:44.340 --> 04:48.360
implementation, distributing funds for infrastructure and climate projects,

04:48.720 --> 04:52.320
cementing regulations. He said he is going to keep fighting for

04:52.320 --> 04:55.420
