04:55.420 --> 04:59.560
economy and trying to lower costs and he'll speak out against extremism and

04:59.560 --> 05:03.600
political violence. And of course, he is still trying very hard to get a

05:03.600 --> 05:07.440
ceasefire for hostages deal in Gaza. Tam, we have a lot of time to talk

05:07.440 --> 05:10.320
about this, but at the end of the day, how do you think his legacy will be

05:10.320 --> 05:13.780
defined? Well, you know, there's been a lot of praise from Democrats about

05:13.780 --> 05:17.700
Biden's selflessness since his announcement on Sunday, but the real

05:17.700 --> 05:21.620
judgment comes in November. By realizing he needed to step aside at this

05:21.620 --> 05:26.120
